Package org.drip.measure.discrete

Class BoundedUniformIntegerDistribution

java.lang.Object
org.drip.measure.continuous.R1Univariate
org.drip.measure.discrete.BoundedUniformIntegerDistribution
public class BoundedUniformIntegerDistribution
extends R1Univariate
BoundedUniformIntegerDistribution implements the Univariate Bounded Uniform Integer Distribution, with the Integer being generated between a (n inclusive) lower and an upper Bound.

  • Module = Computational Core Module
  • Library = Numerical Analysis Library
  • Project = Rd Continuous/Discrete Probability Measures
  • Package = Antithetic, Quadratically Re-sampled, De-biased Distribution
Author:
Lakshmi Krishnamurthy
